{% liquid
    assign heading_text = section.settings.heading_text
    assign short_description = section.settings.short_description
    assign button_text = section.settings.button_text
    assign button_link = section.settings.button_link
%}

<style>
    .{{section.id}}  {
       display: flex;
       justify-content: flex-end;
       align-items: center;
       background: 
        url('{{ "leablack.png" | asset_url }}'),            
        linear-gradient(to right, #e9faff 80%, #e9faff 150%); 
       background-size: contain;  
       background-repeat: no-repeat;
       background-position: left center;
       height: 600px;
       padding: 0; 
       margin: 0 auto; 
      max-width: 1400px; 
    background-color: linear-gradient(#ffffff 50%, #cce7ff 20%);

     }
     .{{section.id}} .herotext{
       max-width: 700px;
     margin-left: auto;
     padding-left: 50px;
     text-align: left;
     margin-right: 20px;
     
     }
     .{{section.id}} .herotext h1{
           font-family: 'Poppins';
           font-weight: 250;
           font-style: normal;
           font-size: 42px;
           line-height: 62px;
           color:black;
         margin-top: -10px;
           
         

     }
     .{{section.id}} .herotext p{
     font-family: 'Work Sans';
     font-weight: 300;
       font-size: 16px;
       line-height: 24px;
       color: black;
       padding-bottom: 5px;
       margin-top: -15px;
       width: 90%;
     }
     /* mobile */
     @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
       .{{section.id}} {
           flex-direction: column;
           align-items: center;
           background: none; 
           height: auto;
           padding: 0;
           max-width: 100%;
       }

       .{{section.id}}::before {
           content: "";
           display: block;
           width: 100%;
           height: 200px; 
           background-image: url('{{ "leablack.png" | asset_url }}');
           background-size: cover;
           background-position: center;
       }

       .{{section.id}} .herotext {
           max-width: 100%;
           padding: 20px;
           text-align: left;
       }

       .{{section.id}} .herotext h1 {
           font-size: 28px;
           line-height: 36px;
           padding-bottom: 20px;
       }

       .{{section.id}} .herotext p {
           font-size: 14px;
           line-height: 20px;


       }
}


</style>

<div>
    <section class="{{section.id}}">
  <div class="herotext">
    <h1>{{ heading_text }}</h1>
    <p>{{ short_description }}</p>
    <button class="button">
      <a href="{{button_link}}">{{ button_text }}</a>
    </button>
  </div>
</section>
</div>


{% schema %}
    {
        "name": "hero-about-lea-black",
        "settings": [
            {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "heading_text",
                "label": "Heading Text",
                "default": "Welcome to the World of Lea Black!"
            },
            
                {
                "type": "richtext",
                "id": "short_description",
                "label": "Short Description",
                "default": "<p>Lea Black’s business focus for more than twenty years has at its core the health, beauty, fitness, and wellness of women everywhere. She has an unparalleled track record of success in developing and marketing natural skincare products made with ethically sourced ingredients before she married and started a family in the ‘90s. Her previous beauty company had offices worldwide with global distribution of over 400 products — including the highly successful “Sudden Youth® Lift Complete Facial Treatment,” which still maintains a strong and loyal consumer demand, and the fragrance “Jazz,” which was sold to YSL.</p><p>Lea Black Beauty® broke boundaries again by developing and launching the hugely popular Lea Black Beauty® CBD Collection in 2019, introducing all the benefits of hemp to her already industry-leading luxury skincare and beauty products.</p><p>Experience the results for yourself with premium, natural skincare products from Lea Black Beauty®.</p>"
                },

             {
                "type": "image_picker",
                "id": "image",
                "label": "Image"
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "button_text",
                "label": "Button Text",
                "default": "SHOP BEAUTY COLLECTION"
            },
            {
                "type": "url",
                "id": "button_link",
                "label": "Button Link"
            }
        ],
            "presets": [
        {
        "name": "hero-about-lea-black",
        "category": "Custom"
    }
]
   }
{% endschema %}